pageContext.claim: “The same thing with that other young gentleman, Miles [Taylor]. I never met him. I don't know him. He's on your network all the time, CNN. I have no idea who he is. It's a terrible thing.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump was not even prompted and he brought up Miles Taylor, a former chief of staff at the Department of Homeland Security. Trump posed for photos with Trump in the Oval Office. Taylor tweeted one of those photos.
